                <h2>Stages of Breast Cancer</h2>
                <p class="lead">There are five stages of breast cancer as follows: <br /> </p>
                <ul class="lead">
                    <li><b>Stage 0 Breast Cancer:</b><br />Stage 0 breast cancer is early stage cancer. </li>
                    <li><b>Stage 1 Breast Cancer:</b><br />In Stage 1 breast cancer, the cancer is still considered in an early stage. </li>
                    <li><b>Stage 2 Breast Cancer:</b><br />In stage 2 breast cancer, the cancer is in the breast and may also be in nearby lymph nodes. </li>
                    <li><b>Stage 3 Breast Cancer:</b><br />In stage 3 breast cancer, cancer hasn’t spread far beyond the breast and nearby lymph nodes. </li>
                    <li><b>Stage 4 Breast Cancer:</b><br />In stage 4 breast cancer, cancer has spread beyond the breast and nearby lymph nodes to other parts of the body. </li>
                </ul>
            </div> <br>
            
